{"tid":1465451,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"機場包圍緊一撚定係鬼 等克警出師有名","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:22.000Z","uid":201220,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f48f0730cc5c7519db6c05bbb5826e301ba9c7de","tid":1465451,"uid":201220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:04:48.000Z","msg":"劇本 如果你真係手足明知機場係和理非回合就唔應該幫手去圍 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">因為過去每一幕一幕好令人難以置信既 而家諗返睇返都好多破綻</span><br />\n所以 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚捉完鬼再圍咁耐 一撚定係鬼 煲撚大件事比克警有位有藉口入黎清場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">因為當捉到鬼之後 大家都約所有注意力放哂落呢隻鬼到 但卻忘記左魔鬼在細節 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">嚴正呼籲 現場真正手足一定要遠離呢次包圍<br />\n因為仆街克警已經出師有名 係咁話係 禁錮</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔該幫手推！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d92aca3a109b1a0ec8918ef6db7716e39c356e7","tid":1465451,"uid":201220,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:06:14.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"65583ac29a005cb8a81a6ce594fee8d65c6894fe","tid":1465451,"uid":201220,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yTde8xX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyTde8xX.jpg&h=64ff8345&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea7a752c43dfb7ff6d507642d54be151b129cf5b","tid":1465451,"uid":201220,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:12:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一幕又一幕 影到有示威者 衝埋去克警私家車<br />\n根本就係魔鬼細節 <br />\n就好似當日破壞的士司機倒後鏡咁 明明大隊都唔會主動破壞 仲要係攻擊克警私家車 因為佢係鬼 有免死金牌</span></span>"},{"pid":"2f225b5fef1c1874d95ab2d8991ed2ee24c8a05e","tid":1465451,"uid":